    "After 50 years, Bellon retired as chairman of Sodexo in January 2016; he remains chairman emeritus. His daughter, Sophie, is now chairwoman.",
    "In 2006, Bellon helped write and edit a book called \"I've Had A Lot Of Fun: The Sodexo Story.\"",
    "He released his second book, \"To Serve And To Grow,\" in 2019, detailing his values and principles of management."
